<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="Author" content="Takatty">
    <meta name="title" content="Sharechat">
    <title></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/chat-text.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/responsive/chat-text-responsive.css'/>
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="header-title">
        <h1>Room Name</h1>
        <p>このページでは、チャットメッセージの編集や削除が選択出来ます。</p>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="chat">
        <div class="chat-show">
          <div class="chat-people">
            <div class="chat-people-img">
              <p>
                <img src="/images/human.png" width="130" height="130">
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-people-name">
              <p><%= user.name %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-content">
            <div class="chat-mess">
              <p><%= text.text %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="buttoms">
              <p>
                <input type="button" value="前のページへ戻る" onclick="history.back()">
              </p>
              <p>
                <input type="button" value="<%= edit_bottom %>" onClick="location.href='/chat/room/<%= text.room_id %>/text/<%= text.message_id %>/account/<%= text.user_id %>/edit'" class="account-bottom">
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>